arStrings.szText: "Do you want this vial of curious venom?"
What is it now? A curious kind of venom, from the Nangari... I see.
You know, this is their place. We all came here from elsewhere. But not them, no.
Even I don't know how long they've been here, or how they came to be.
This venom is clear because the Nangari it came from is about to begin molting. Or at least it was, I assume... you must have killed it? Yes, of course.
Perhaps the seasonal molt will begin soon. It's said to be lucky to keep some in your house, but it's only lucky if it's not full of parasites. That's what I always say.
